pull.title: BIP 173: Adds link to SLIP-0173
pull.body: SLIP-0173 lists registered human-readable parts for BIP-0173, keeping the BIPs free of other cryptocurrency information. This echoes SLIP/BIP-0044 with registered coin types for HD wallet derivation paths.

events.message:
Adds link to SLIP-0173

Fix typo

events.body:
Rebased on top of `master`.

Coming up on one-year anniversary of this PR. Can we get some forward motion here?
